PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780481194
OL,3,CHealth Secretary: I would no longer
OL,4,Csay trans women are women
OL,6,FHealth Secretary and Ealing North MP
OL,7,FJames Murray said it is "absolutely
OL,8,Fclear" that single-sex spaces within
OL,9,Fthe NHS should be "protected on the
OL,10,Fbasis of sex" as he confirmed he would
OL,11,Fno longer use the phrase "trans women
OL,12,Fare women".
OL,14,FMr Murray, who was appointed to the
OL,15,Frole last month after the resignation
OL,16,Fof Wes Streeting, said he recognises
OL,17,Fthat "sex and gender are different
OL,18,Fthings".
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@FO]qD@SOUrD@MO]sD@ZOUtD@JO]yD@
OL,26,AFOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
