OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780481194
OL,3,CHealth Secretary: I would no longer
OL,4,Csay trans women are women
OL,6,FIn May, the Government published long-
OL,7,Fawaited guidance drafted by Britain's
OL,8,Frights watchdog which confirmed single-
OL,9,Fsex services must be on the basis of
OL,10,Fbiological sex.
OL,12,FThe Equality and Human Rights
OL,13,FCommission (EHRC) guidance stated: "In
OL,14,Fseparate or single-sex services, a
OL,15,Ftrans man will be excluded from the
OL,16,Fmen-only service because his sex is
OL,17,Ffemale, and a trans woman will be
OL,18,Fexcluded from the women-only service
OL,19,Fbecause her sex is male."
OL,26,@uD@dOU{D@YO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780481194
OL,3,CHealth Secretary: I would no longer
OL,4,Csay trans women are women
OL,6,FIt covered a range of scenarios
OL,7,Fincluding hospital wards, which it
OL,8,Fsaid can lawfully exclude trans
OL,9,Fpatients if single-sex.
OL,11,FThe code states that hospitals can
OL,12,Fchoose to provide a single-sex ward
OL,13,F"for women patients to protect their
OL,14,Fsafety, privacy and dignity".
OL,16,FIf they do, it has to be on the basis
OL,17,Fof a patient's biological sex.
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
