OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780481194
OL,3,CHealth Secretary: I would no longer
OL,4,Csay trans women are women
OL,6,FUnder current NHS guidance, trans
OL,7,Fpatients can be accommodated on single-
OL,8,Fsex wards based on the gender they
OL,9,Fidentify as.
OL,11,FWhen the code was published, just
OL,12,Funder two weeks ago, an NHS
OL,13,Fspokesperson said: "Now that the
OL,14,FEquality and Human Rights Commission's
OL,15,Fstatutory guidance has been laid in
OL,16,FParliament, we are reviewing it with
OL,17,Fthe aim of publishing draft guidance
OL,18,Ffor the health service shortly."
OL,26,@uD@TOUzD@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
