OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780481194
OL,3,CHealth Secretary: I would no longer
OL,4,Csay trans women are women
OL,6,FThe code of practice, which would
OL,7,Fapply across England, Scotland and
OL,8,FWales, was laid before Parliament on
OL,9,FMay 21 for scrutiny from both MPs in
OL,10,Fthe Commons and peers in the Lords.
OL,12,FIt will not be enacted for 40 days.
OL,14,FWhile a vote would not be required to
OL,15,Fenact the code and make it statutory,
OL,16,Feither House could pass a motion to
OL,17,Freject it within that period.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
