PN,40809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780481194
OL,3,CHealth Secretary: I would no longer
OL,4,Csay trans women are women
OL,6,FThe updated guidance was published
OL,7,Fmore than a year after a landmark
OL,8,FSupreme Court ruling in April 2025
OL,9,Fwhich said the words "woman" and "sex"
OL,10,Fin the Equality Act 2010 refer to a
OL,11,Fbiological woman and biological sex.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
